io.proximax.dfms.privacy

Interface PrivacyStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomPrivacyStrategy, PasswordPrivacyStrategy, PlainPrivacyStrategy, ProximaXKeysPrivacyStrategy, ShamirSecretSharingPrivacyStrategy

    public interface PrivacyStrategy
    The privacy strategy interface

    Privacy strategy handles the encrypting and decrypting of data

    When creating a custom Privacy Strategy, implement CustomPrivacyStrategy
    See Also:
